Package: hkmeans
Type: Package
Title: Divisive hierarchical k-means clustering
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Shaun Wilkinson [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Shaun Wilkinson <shaunpwilkinson@gmail.com>
Description: Contains a single function 'hkmeans' for divisive clustering based on 
    recursive k-means partitioning (k = 2). Useful for clustering large datasets
    where computation of a n x n distance matrix is not feasible (e.g. n > 10,000 records).
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: http://github.com/shaunpwilkinson/hkmeans
BugReports: http://github.com/shaunpwilkinson/hkmeans/issues
Imports: 
    openssl,
    phylogram
